  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK279">
<l>kaṇaikoṭiti yāḻkōṭu cevvitāṅ kaṉṉa</l>
<l>viṉaipaṭu pālāṟ koḷal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As, in its use, the arrow is crooked, and the curved lute is straight, so by their deeds, (and not by their appearance) let (the uprightness or crookedness of) men be estimated.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
